Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 02 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Fracture' from the indication dropdown menu
Then 'Add indication' button is enabled

And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled
And 'Exclusion' radio button is enabled

And 'Radius' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ulna' checkbox is enabled
And 'Carpalia' checkbox is enabled
And 'Metacarpalia/Phalanges' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Suspicion of' radio button
Then 'Occult' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Exclusion' radio button
Then 'Occult' checkbox is enabled
